
    1) Create card using database

         a) Word selection from dropdown menu:
             - "ab" characters typing
             - dropdown menu has shown
             - select a word in a dropdown menu
             - wordAutoCompleteTextView shows selected word

         b) Select a translation in list extracted from database
             - click translationSpinner
             - click on the item in a dropdown menu
             - clicked item is in the translationSpinner

         c) Select an example pair(sentence - translation) in a list extracted from database
             - click exampleSpinner
             - click on the item in a dropdown menu
             - clicked item is in the exampleSpinner

         d) Select image in an imageSpinner, filled by image Api
             - click imageSpinner
             - click the image in a dropdown menu
             - selected image is in a collapsed imageSpinner

         e) Select a group title
             - type group name first two characters
             - select a group name in a dropdown menu
             - check: wordAutoCompleteTextView shows selected word

         f) createButton click appends new card to cardGroupFragment
             - click create button
             - cardGroupFragment inflation
             - check a new card view presence, mapping selected on card creation:
                    word, translation, example, image, group name;

